{"tid":1122340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門山景邨女子高處墮下 當場死亡","createTime":"2019-04-24T01:40:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T04:35:15.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"11f560d06a9b19be7a21ab52af406c68435ddb21","tid":1122340,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T01:40:05.000Z","msg":"屯門山景邨有女子從高處墮下，當場死亡，警方初步調查相信事件無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n事發在凌晨1時許，景安樓一名女子突然由高處墮下，倒臥對開行人通道簷篷頂，其家人發現後報警。消防到場將女子救下，救護員檢驗後證實女事主已經死亡。警方經初步調查後，相信事件無可疑。據悉，女事主有身體病紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰ <br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 23892222 <br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(24小時中文及多種語言)： 28960000 <br />\n醫管局精神健康專線(24小時諮詢)：24667350 <br />\n生命熱線： 23820000 <br />\n社會福利署： 23432255<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1485702/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1485702%2F&d=zdm3SfM4sEUVnXmiquxubDH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=9fff9956\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1485702%2F&h=7173c602\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1485702/</a>"},{"pid":"069b0cbbfcd4e22022dd065535e89133a21f0307","tid":1122340,"uid":90820,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T02:08:39.000Z","msg":"爭啲以為舊聞嚟<br />\n日日都有人自殺<br />\n睇新聞睇到麻木咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"247d70a373b22269ba0399991b1c238336075bd5","tid":1122340,"uid":51615,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T02:10:58.000Z","msg":"山景真係每年都有幾單跳樓<br />\n呢條邨真係堅邪！"},{"pid":"fadd57ca65b70eee28cebfb781a7fa2c3ac8c1bd","tid":1122340,"uid":57462,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T02:11:39.000Z","msg":"早十年就澤豐<br />\n宜家就山景安定膽拖友愛"},{"pid":"14d42ab2f3f26db96f28bb61ca45833a4e04cc90","tid":1122340,"uid":90820,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fadd57ca65b70eee28cebfb781a7fa2c3ac8c1bd","tid":1122340,"ui